title: David Guetta - Listen (Deluxe Version) (2014) iTunes [Nativedoll
description:
This is redone, my first one had a track missing. iTunes recognized the song as the same exact one as the Single and didn't add one of them. It doesn't like duplicates, I guess. Thank you to the person letting me know this, I'm human, I make mistakes too. Enjoy! Please seed and vote, it'll make me a very happy Hattepaa (Coyote)! ^^

Very sorry again! I will try my best to quadruple check the tracks!
